query:
SELECT 
  i.inspectionDate,
  t.legacyLocationId,
  t.component,
  t.location,
  t.stationKey,
  t.componentGroup,
  t.tActual
FROM tmlReadings t
JOIN inspections i ON t.inspectionId = i.id
WHERE i.vesselTagNumber = '54-11-001'
ORDER BY i.inspectionDate, t.legacyLocationId
LIMIT 20;
